{SOLDIER SCREAMS}

63
00:05:13,346 --> 00:05:14,654
{CREATURE BELLOWS}

64
00:05:21,587 --> 00:05:23,396
{SOLDIERS SCREAMING}

65
00:05:28,361 --> 00:05:30,466
