You know that, you have instincts.

145
00:14:50,055 --> 00:14:52,057
The sun of a god.

146
00:14:54,293 --> 00:14:56,364
A sun needs a father.

147
00:14:56,929 --> 00:14:58,101
I made a vow to la.

148
