as a simple fisherman.

151
00:15:08,574 --> 00:15:12,750
Well, that's a fine game in normal times.

152
00:15:13,212 --> 00:15:16,193
But if you have power, you also have a duty.

153
00:15:17,616 --> 00:15:19,425
Just fix my body...

154
00:15:19,919 --> 00:15:21,762
...and leave my soul to me.

155
00:15:22,454 --> 00:15:23,933
{GROANS}

156
00:15:28,093 --> 00:15:29,595
Where are we going?

157
00:15:30,996 --> 00:15:33,203
I need to speak to my father.

158
