172
00:16:40,199 --> 00:16:43,305
- I fear the worst.
- Here, here.

173
00:16:43,769 --> 00:16:46,181
I got you, I got you.

174
00:16:47,039 --> 00:16:48,347
{POSEIDON GROANS}

175
00:16:49,475 --> 00:16:51,079
