182
00:17:11,597 --> 00:17:12,940
I'm only half a god.

183
00:17:13,165 --> 00:17:15,167
Then you must find another half-god.

184
00:17:16,335 --> 00:17:17,678
Agenor.

185
00:17:18,237 --> 00:17:19,841
