191
00:17:42,828 --> 00:17:43,465
If my sun...

192
00:17:43,629 --> 00:17:46,235
...survives and proves worthy...

193
00:17:46,832 --> 00:17:48,470
...give it to him.

194
00:18:12,558 --> 00:18:15,164
{CREATURES CHITTERING}

195
