251
00:22:57,743 --> 00:23:00,053
This is a battlefield.

252
00:23:00,245 --> 00:23:02,555
- I am in command here.
- Uh-huh.

253
00:23:03,248 --> 00:23:05,057
Well, I wish to speak to the queen.

254
00:23:05,217 --> 00:23:07,561
And the queen wishes to speak to you.

255
00:23:09,554 --> 00:23:10,794
Your Majesty.

256
